019 All-Pro Team|All-Pro]] (2019) <ref name=\"2019probowl\">{{cite web|title=2019 AP NFL All-Pro team rosters and voting |url=https://apnews.com/eeca59cc33eb5eeb11f3d08e7b0328c1 |website=apnews.com\n|publisher=Associated Press |accessdate=3 January 2020}}</ref>\n* [[Sporting News]] Offensive Player of the Year (2019)<ref>{{cite web |title=NFL awards: Resurgent 49ers dominate voting for Sporting News\u2019 2019 honors |url=https://www.sportingnews.com/us/nfl/news/nfl-awards-2019-voting-49ers-honors/tbjtlf3c3qal13gnioqh4p65l |website=sportingnews.com |publisher=Sporting News |accessdate=5 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n====NFL records====\n* First player to throw 30 touchdowns and rush for 1,000 yards in a single season<ref>{{cite web |title=Lamar Jackson Broke Another Record And He\u2019s The 1st One To Do This In The NFL |url=https://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2019/12/18/ravens-lamar-jackson-record-nfl/ |website=baltimore.cbslocal.com |publisher=CBS Baltimore wjz-tv |accessdate=December 19, 2019}}</ref>\n* First player to throw for at least 250 yards and rush for at least 120 yards in the same regular-season game: Week 2, 2019<ref name=\"Platko\"/>\n* First player to throw for at least 200 yards and rush for at least 150 yards in the same regular-season game: Week 6, 2019<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000001065681/article/lamar-jackson-sets-records-in-dualthreat-performance | title=Lamar Jackson sets records in dual-threat performance | website=NFL.com | date=October 14, 2019 | access-date=October 14, 2019 | author=Patra, Kevin}}</ref>\n* First player to complete at least 75% of his throws with 12+ touchdown passes over a three-game span<ref name=\"sunstaff\">{{cite web |last1=Baltimore Sun Staff |title=Lamar Jackson watch: The most mind-boggling stats from Ravens QB\u2019s historic start to career |url=https://www.baltimoresun.com/sports/ravens/bs-sp-ravens-lamar-jackson-watch-week-13-rams-20191126-v4ad7qth4rbdfdqmy4htfkq724-story.html |website=balti