other Playoff Loss|url=https://www.baltimoreravens.com/news/lamar-jackson-shakes-off-haters-after-another-playoff-loss|publisher=Baltimore Ravens|website=BaltimoreRavens.com|date=January 12, 2020|accessdate=January 18, 2020}}</ref>\n* First quarterback to finish a game with a [[perfect passer rating]] (minimum 15 attempts), at least 50 yards rushing and one touchdown run<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.espn.com/nfl/story/_/id/28051772/lamar-jackson-joins-elite-club-perfect-passer-rating |title=Jackson joins elite club with perfect passer rating |last=Hensley |first=Jamison |date=November 10, 2019 |website=ESPN.com |language=en |access-date=November 20, 2019}}</ref>\n* First quarterback with five 100-yard rushing games in a season (2019)<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.espn.com/nfl/recap?gameId=401128027 |title=Jackson, Ravens beat 49ers 20-17 to extend win streak to 8 |agency=Associated Press |website=ESPN.com |date=December 1, 2019 |accessdate=December 2, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"8Lamar\">{{cite web |title=8 Lamar Jackson |url=http://ftp.ravenspr.com/bio_updates_player/jackson_lamar.pdf |website=baltimoreravens.com |publisher=Baltimore Ravens |accessdate=December 26, 2019}}</ref>\n* First quarterback with 1,000+ yards rushing and a 100+ passer rating in a season.<ref name=\"best?\">{{cite web |last1=Hensley |first1=Jamison |title=Is Lamar Jackson putting up the best season ever at quarterback? |url=https://www.espn.com/blog/baltimore-ravens/post/_/id/51507/is-lamar-jackson-working-on-the-best-season-ever-for-a-qb |website=espn.com |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=6 January 2020}}</ref>\n* Most rushing yards by a quarterback in a season: 1,206 (2019)<ref name=favorite/><ref name=\"vickrecord\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.espn.com/nfl/story/_/id/28285951/ravens-qb-lamar-jackson-breaks-michael-vick-single-season-rushing-yards-record |title=Ravens QB Lamar Jackson breaks Michael Vick's single-season rushing yards record |last=Hensley |first=Jamison |date=December 12, 2019 |w