26/ravens-lamar-jackson-passes-michael-vick-madden-fastest-qb |title=Ravens' Lamar Jackson passes Michael Vick as Madden's fastest QB |last=Hensley |first=Jamison |date=November 26, 2019 |website=espn.com |publisher=ESPN |access-date=November 27, 2019}}</ref>\n* Youngest player with 5 touchdown passes in multiple games.<ref name=ravensrecords/>\n* Youngest quarterback to ever start a playoff game: 21 years, 364 days (2018 Wild Card Round against the Los Angeles Chargers)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000001007284/article/lamar-jackson-will-be-youngest-qb-to-start-in-playoffs |title=Lamar Jackson will be youngest QB to start in playoffs |first=Kevin |last=Patra |date=January 3, 2019 |access-date=November 26, 2019}}</ref>\n* Youngest quarterback to achieve a [[perfect passer rating]]: 22 years, 244 days (Week 1, 2019)<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbssports.com/nfl/news/lamar-jackson-joined-an-elite-group-of-super-bowl-winning-quarterbacks-with-week-1-performance/ |title=Lamar Jackson joined an elite group of Super Bowl winning quarterbacks with Week 1 performance |last=Kerr |first=Jeff |date=September 9, 2019 |website=CBSSports.com |language=en |access-date=October 1, 2019}}</ref>\n* Youngest quarterback to start a Pro Bowl game.<ref name=2020pro/>\n* Highest touchdown passing percentage (7.4%) in the Super Bowl Era (minimum 500 attempts)<ref>{{cite web |title=For combined seasons, from 1970 to 2019 |url=https://www.pro-football-reference.com/play-index/psl_finder.cgi?request=1&match=combined&year_min=1970&year_max=2019&season_start=1&season_end=-1&pos%5B%5D=qb&draft_year_min=1936&draft_year_max=2017&draft_slot_min=1&draft_slot_max=500&draft_pick_in_round=pick_overall&conference=any&draft_pos%5B%5D=qb&draft_pos%5B%5D=rb&draft_pos%5B%5D=wr&draft_pos%5B%5D=te&draft_pos%5B%5D=e&draft_pos%5B%5D=t&draft_pos%5B%5D=g&draft_pos%5B%5D=c&draft_pos%5B%5D=ol&draft_pos%5B%5D=dt&draft_pos%5B%5D=de&draft_pos%5B%5D=dl&draft_pos%5B%5D=ilb&draft_pos%5B%5D=olb