cle |access-date=November 28, 2019}}</ref>\n* Most games with a perfect passer rating: 2<ref name=\"super8\">{{cite web |title=8 Lamar Jackson Bio |url=http://ftp.ravenspr.com/bio_updates_player/jackson_lamar.pdf |website=baltimoreravens.com |publisher=Baltimore Ravens |accessdate=November 29, 2019}}</ref>\n* Most passing touchdowns in a game: 5 (tied with [[Joe Flacco]] and [[Tony Banks (American football)|Tony Banks]])<ref name=super8/>\n* Most games with 5 passing touchdowns: 3<ref name=super8/>\n* Most touchdown passes in the first (n) games of a season (all 2019): \n** First game: 5\n** First 2 games: 7 \n** First 3 games: 7 (tied with [[Joe Flacco]])\n** First 4 games: 10\n** First 5 games: 11\n** First 11 games: 24 (tied with [[Vinny Testaverde]])\n** First 12 games: 25\n** First 13 games: 28\n** First 14 games: 33\n** First 15 games: 36\n* Highest completion percentage in a game: 88.2<ref name=super8/>\n* Highest completion percentage in a season: 66.1 (2019)<ref>{{cite web |title=Baltimore Ravens Single-Season Passing Leaders |url=https://www.pro-football-reference.com/teams/rav/single-season-passing.htm |website=pro-football-reference.com |publisher=Pro Football Reference |accessdate=3 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Highest passer rating in a season: 113.3 (2019)<ref name=8Lamar/>\n* Highest touchdown/pass percentage in a season; 9% (2019)<ref name=8Lamar/>\n\n==Popular culture==\n{{external media\n| float  = right\n| width  = 300px\n| video1 =[https://www.baltimoreravens.com/video/final-drive-here-s-a-teaser-of-lamar-jackson-on-celebrity-family-feud-x1092 Lamar Jackson on Celebrity Family Feud], Baltimore Ravens video\n}}\nPrior to the start of the 2019 NFL season, Jackson appeared on [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]'s ''[[Celebrity Family Feud]]'', pitting current NFL players against former NFL players.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.baltimoresun.com/sports/ravens/bs-sp-ravens-lamar-jackson-family-feud-20190226-story.html |title=Ravens quarterback Lamar 